title: SMC_INCSymbolTable (Interface)
text:
INTERFACE SMC_INCSymbolTable
Interface for a symbol table that can be used to look up global
variables and CNC sub program signatures.
Methods:
GetSubprogramSignature
LookupGlobalVar
StoreSubprogramSignature
Structure:
GetSubprogramSignature (Method)
LookupGlobalVar (Method)
StoreSubprogramSignature (Method)
